&lt;p&gt;We are looking for an enthusiastic, committed and experienced Registered Nurse to join our busy Endoscopy Unit at Homerton University Hospital NHS Foundation Trust. Our unit is JAG accredited.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This post offers the candidate the opportunity to learn or enhance their existing skills in caring for patients undergoing investigative procedures and treatments as well as providing support for the patient and their family.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Additional support and training will also be provided to ensure the post holder can deputise for unit manager as required.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful candidate will need to be able to work effectively as part of multi-disciplinary team, demonstrating excellent interpersonal skills and demonstrate a willingness to learn and further develop their career.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Please note this post is for day shifts only Monday - Sunday as required.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Interview Date: TBC&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Working Hours: 37.5 hours per week&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Name: Jason Harvey&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Job title: Charge Nurse&lt;/p&gt;
